Payment and Cancellations 
The annual membership fee will be automatically billed after the first 7-day trial period to the chosen payment method on an annual recurring basis - as authorized upon membership registration. Ubuy is not responsible for any additional charges or fees incurred by the customer's bank or credit card. The membership fee is non-refundable. 
Renewal & Cancellations 
Unless the customer cancels 
their membership plan 30 days prior to the end of the applicable membership period, Ubuy will automatically renew the membership at the end of the applicable membership period - as agreed upon registration - through the chosen payment method. 
If renewal fails 
due to issues in the customer's payment method or expired credentials and the customer does not provide a new eligible payment method, the membership plan will be automatically canceled. If the customer provides a new payment method other than the original payment method provided during the registration stage and the renewal is successful, the new membership period will be based on the original membership date. 
If the customer cancels auto-renewal

text:
Shop the Best Yoga Straps Online
Explore A Wide Range of Yoga Straps in Mexico
At Ubuy, we offer a diverse selection of yoga straps to enhance your exercise and fitness routines. Whether you're a beginner or an experienced yogi, our high-quality straps are designed to provide optimal support and help you deepen your stretches and poses.
Improve Flexibility and Alignment with Yoga Straps
Yoga straps are versatile tools that can greatly assist in improving flexibility and alignment during your yoga practice. They allow you to easily reach and hold challenging poses, encouraging a deeper stretch and preventing strain or injury. Our straps are made from durable materials and come in various lengths to accommodate different body types and levels of flexibility.
Enhance Your Yoga Practice with Premium Quality Straps
When it comes to yoga straps, quality matters. That's why Ubuy offers only premium quality straps from reputable brands. Our straps are made to withstand regular use and feature sturdy buckles or D-ring closures for secure and adjustable fastening. With a wide range of colors and designs available, you can choose a strap that not only enhances your practice but also reflects your personal style.
Benefits of Using Yoga Straps
Using yoga straps in your practice can provide numerous benefits. They not only help improve flexibility and alignment but also assist in deepening stretches, increasing range of motion, and building strength. Yoga straps are particularly beneficial for beginners, allowing them to gradually improve their flexibility over time. Additionally, these straps can be used for restorative poses and modifications, making them suitable for individuals of all fitness levels.
Versatile and Functional Straps for Every Yoga Style
No matter which style of yoga you practice, our wide range of straps can support your needs. From gentle Hatha yoga to more dynamic practices like Vinyasa or Power yoga, our straps offer the versatility and functionality required for various poses and sequences. Whether you're using a strap to lengthen your reach in seated forward bends or to deepen your backbends, you can rely on our selection of straps to enhance your yoga experience.
Frequently Asked Questions About Yoga Straps 
How do yoga straps help in improving flexibility?
Yoga straps assist in improving flexibility by allowing you to deepen your stretches and gradually extend your range of motion. By using a strap, you can safely and effectively move further into poses and hold them for longer periods, which helps increase flexibility over time.
Are yoga straps suitable for beginners?
Yes, yoga straps are highly beneficial for beginners. They provide support and stability, helping beginners gradually improve their flexibility and perform poses with correct alignment. Straps allow beginners to comfortably reach and hold positions that may otherwise be challenging.
Can I use yoga straps for other exercises besides yoga?
Yes, yoga straps can be used for a variety of exercises besides yoga. They are commonly used in Pilates, physical therapy, and general stretching routines. The versatility of yoga straps allows for targeted stretching and improved alignment in various fitness activities.
What length of yoga strap should I choose?
The length of the yoga strap depends on personal preference and body type. Longer straps (around 8 feet) offer more versatility and are suitable for taller individuals or poses that require a larger range of motion. Shorter straps (around 6 feet) are ideal for individuals with a smaller build or for specific poses that require less length.
Are the buckles or D-ring closures on the straps secure?
Yes, the buckles or D-ring closures on our yoga straps are designed to be secure and reliable. They ensure that the strap remains firmly in place during your practice without slipping or loosening. You can have peace of mind knowing that your strap will provide the necessary support throughout your yoga session.
Can I wash my yoga strap?
Most yoga straps are made from washable materials, such as cotton or nylon. Check the care instructions provided by the manufacturer to determine the best method for cleaning your specific strap. In general, handwashing with mild soap and air drying is recommended to maintain the integrity and longevity of the strap.
Do yoga straps come in different colors and designs?
Yes, at Ubuy, we offer a wide range of yoga strap colors and designs. You can choose from vibrant and eye-catching options or opt for more subtle and neutral tones. The variety of colors and designs allows you to select a strap that suits your personal style and enhances your yoga practice.
Are yoga straps suitable for individuals with limited mobility?
Absolutely. Yoga straps are particularly beneficial for individuals with limited mobility or those recovering from injuries. They provide support and increased stability, allowing individuals to participate in yoga poses and stretches with proper form and reduced strain. Consult with a healthcare professional to determine the best way to incorporate yoga straps into your exercise routine.

Shop Premium Beauty and Personal Care Products Online at Ubuy Mexico
Beauty and personal care is a giant industry now with growing online shopping trends. If you want to enhance your overall appearance and promote self-confidence, beauty and personal care products are a must. These products ensure the hygiene and well-being of the body and make it more attractive. 
Personal and beauty care products include soaps, shampoos, toothpaste, deodorants, etc. A large collection of these products is available online for sale at Ubuy. The beauty section is stacked up with products like makeup, lipsticks, mascaras, nail polishes, beard wax, hair gels and more. Get Top Rated Beauty and Personal Care Products at Ubuy Mexico
Searching for luxury beauty and products to maintain your beauty and personal hygiene? Pick the most popular and useful products for skin care, hair care, oral care, and fragrances from global brands and order them online.
Haircare
Healthy and attractive hairs are the keys to boosted confidence and high self-esteem. Washing, conditioning and styling your hair are necessary to bring that self-confidence from inside. Explore this extensive haircare section and select your favourite products from the top brands.
Shampoos
Our hair gets excess oil from sebum that clogs pores and causes dandruff, itching and similar problems. Shampoos remove excess oil, dirt and other impurities from hair and scalp to reduce hair problems. They also promote hair growth and make them shiny and smooth. Discover a wide range of natural and organic shampoos with unique qualities to keep your hair healthy and natural.
Conditioners
Conditioners play a crucial role in maintaining a healthy look and appearance of hair. These remove excess oil from hair while washing and replenish moisture lost due to shampoos. As a result, they provide frizz-free, soft, shiny, and manageable hair. They simply detangle hair and minimise split ends and breakage. Protection against heat damage by styling tools is another benefit you get from conditioners. Go through the entire range of protein conditioners, sulfate-free, and natural conditioners from leading brands and shop them online.
Hair Oil
We must maintain a good oil balance in our hair, like our skin. Hair oils nourish and moisturise dry hairs to give them a shiny, beautiful appearance. They minimise frizz and flyaways, leading to healthy hair growth. Hair oils contain natural vitamins and minerals that keep the scalp calm and irritation-free. They fight against problems like hair damage, hair loss, breakage, and scalp itching and promote healthy growth. Discover argan oil, jojoba oil, olive oil, rosemary oil, and a variety of other natural hair oils here, and select the best one for your hair type.
Hair Masks
A healthy hair care routine involves hair masks to provide intense moisture, nourishment and protection. They lock moisture and hydration in hair to give a frizz-free, shiny and moisturised look for a longer time. Dryness, damage, and dandruff are additional concerns that can be alleviated by using hair masks. They also work on repairing and restoring damaged hair to retain a healthy look. Here, you can find a variety of moisturising masks, colour-protecting masks, and protein masks. Choose the one that best fits your needs and have it shipped right to your door.
Hair Colour
The hair colours enhance self-confidence and impart a perfect styling in the personality of individuals having discoloured or faded hair. Hair colours are an outstanding solution for covering grey, excessive pigment and uneven tones. They are also an important part of personal grooming and are the right way of self-expression. Sometimes, hair colours are used to restore the original hair colour, which is lost during styling and hairdressing processes. A wide range of natural hair colours and dyed hair colours are available in different shades and tones here. Choose the right hair colour to retain attractive and youthful looks and buy it online.
Skincare
Skincare products are typically used to maintain and promote healthy, glowing skin. It is a huge section covering an extensive range of products related to body, face, lip and eye care. They contain a perfect blend of ingredients to cleanse, nourish, and protect skin from damage. These products also work to fight skin ageing by improving skin texture and reducing fine lines and wrinkles for youthful skin. This skincare section is stocked with body scrubs, body washes, face moisturisers, face cleansers, face creams, eye gels and whatnot. Browse the entire list of skin care products from renowned brands like Drunk Elephant and experience a rejuvenated skin feel.
Makeup
The makeup section's name reflects its purpose. Makeup and cosmetic products are used to highlight natural features and enhance the beauty of an individual. As an international ecommerce store, Ubuy stays up-to-date with the latest trends in the sports outdoors industry. Make the Most of Your Outdoor Adventures
With Ubuy, you can make the most of your outdoor adventures. We offer a wide range of products to enhance your experience and ensure your safety and comfort. Whether you need camping essentials, hiking gear, water sports equipment, or any other outdoor accessories, our collection has got you covered. Shop now and embark on unforgettable adventures with confidence.
Frequently Asked Questions About Sports & Outdoors 
What are the essential items for camping?
When it comes to camping, there are a few essential items that you should always have. These include a tent, sleeping bag, camping stove, cooler, and flashlight. Additionally, it's important to pack food, water, and appropriate clothing for the weather conditions.
What type of shoes are best for hiking?
For hiking, it's important to choose footwear that provides comfort, support, and traction. The best hiking shoes or boots are usually made of durable and water-resistant materials. Look for shoes with a sturdy sole, arch support, and ankle protection for added stability on uneven terrain.
How do I choose the right size bicycle?
Choosing the right size bicycle is essential for a comfortable and safe riding experience. To determine the correct bike size, consider your height, inseam measurement, and the type of bike you want. Refer to the manufacturer's sizing chart and recommendations to find the appropriate frame size for your body proportions.
What is the difference between a kayak and a canoe?
The main difference between a kayak and a canoe is their design and seating position. Kayaks usually have a closed cockpit with the paddler sitting inside and using a double-bladed paddle. Canoes, on the other hand, have an open design with the paddler kneeling or sitting on a raised seat and using a single-bladed paddle.
What are the essential fitness accessories for home workouts?
For home workouts, there are several essential fitness accessories that can enhance your exercise routine. These include resistance bands, dumbbells or kettlebells, a yoga mat, a stability ball, and a skipping rope. Additionally, you may consider investing in a workout bench or an exercise bike for more versatility.
What safety gear is necessary for water sports activities?
When participating in water sports activities, it's important to prioritize safety. Essential safety gear may include a life jacket or personal flotation device (PFD), a wetsuit or rash guard for thermal protection, a helmet for water sports such as kayaking or rafting, and a whistle or signaling device for emergencies.
What type of apparel is suitable for winter outdoor activities?
For winter outdoor activities, it's important to dress appropriately to stay warm and comfortable. Layering is key, starting with a moisture-wicking base layer, followed by insulating mid-layers, and finishing with a waterproof and windproof outer shell. Don't forget to wear thermal socks, gloves, a hat, and a scarf to protect extremities from the cold.
How do I determine the right size backpack for hiking?
To determine the right size backpack for hiking, consider the duration of your hikes and the amount of gear you need to carry. A general rule is to choose a backpack with a capacity between 30 and 50 liters for day hikes, and 50 to 80 liters for multi-day hikes. It's also important to ensure a proper fit by adjusting the straps and distributing the weight evenly.

Explore Different Types of Energy Drinks Online
Energy drinks come in various types, each designed to meet different needs and preferences. From traditional energy drinks loaded with caffeine and sugar to natural, organic options with plant-based ingredients, there's something for everyone. Whether you're looking for a quick boost, a performance enhancer, or a healthier alternative, exploring the types of energy drinks helps you find the right fit for your lifestyle.
Traditional Energy Drinks
Traditional energy drinks give immediate energy boosts through caffeine and essential vitamins, together with sugar intake. Energy drinks provide immediate attention enhancement as they combat tiredness, resulting in their popularity among people who need instant energy boosts. The fitness-oriented drink producer Celsius presents consumers with a health-oriented product that provides similar energy benefits.
Sugar-Free Energy Drinks
People who consume sugar carefully can access numerous low-sugar energy drinks that are decent alternatives to regular choices. Through their sugar-free formula, sugar-free energy drinks provide performance enhancement similar to conventional energy drinks. Energy beverages provide vitamins, minerals, and natural fruit flavours, offering a balanced, salt-free alternative to classic energy drinks.
Performance Energy Drinks
Performance energy drinks are explicitly created for people engaged in athletic activities and fitness training. Sports drinks contain electrolytes together with amino acids and high caffeine levels to increase stamina while aiding in recovery after exercise. Energy drinks for athletes are specifically formulated to fuel endurance, boost performance, and replenish nutrients lost during intense physical activity. 
Functional Energy Drinks
Energy drinks function as functional beverages by enhancing cognitive operation, improving wellness features, and strengthening the immune system. Different varieties of healthy energy drinks use adaptogens, nootropics, and natural caffeine molecules to deliver advantages to users. Red Bull stands out as a leading energy drink because it enhances attention and revitalises energy stores, which draws numerous customers who are looking to perk up quickly. People seeking control over their energy drink creation can use powdered drink mixes & flavourings to mix energy-boosting ingredients and desired flavours with nutrients in the water.
Energy Shots
Energy booster drinks comprise energy shots and other portable beverages packed with maximum potency for delivering quick bursts of energy. The beverage formula includes caffeine and B vitamins, along with other substances that enhance focus abilities and stamina duration. The small sizes of energy booster drinks enable portability, so users can easily consume them when they are on the move.
These shots are energy drinks for gamers. Energy booster drinks provide quick workplace energy and pre-workout power for enhanced performance. Buy energy drinks online from Monster Energy, a popular brand in the energy drink market. It is known for its bold flavours and powerful energy boost, making it a favourite choice for many.
Natural and Organic Energy Drinks 
Natural energy drinks, along with their organic counterparts, are healthier beverage options than soda soft drinks because they contain pure plant-based substances, such as green tea, yerba mate, and organic fruit juices. Drinks without artificial additives and preservatives supply environmentally friendly energy enhancement. The drinks elevate alertness, and focus yet do not cause the downhill effect that follows typical sugary soda beverages. 
Related Brands : Red Bull | Monster Energy | Celsius | Prime | NOS | Ghost

What’s the Best Energy Drink for Workouts or Sports?
The best energy drinks for workouts or sports are those with electrolytes and moderate caffeine, like Gatorade or Bodyarmor. These help improve hydration and provide a quick energy boost.
How Do I Choose the Right Energy Drink for My Needs?
To choose the right energy drink, consider the ingredients—look for ones with caffeine for energy, electrolytes for hydration, and no added sugars. Match the drink to your activity level and workout needs.
Where Can I Get Bulk Discounts on Energy Drinks?

Sports drinks are designed to replenish electrolytes and hydrate, while energy drinks contain stimulants like caffeine for a quick energy boost. Sports drinks are better for endurance, while energy drinks are ideal for short bursts of energy.

Prime Hydration is a sports and energy drink brand co-founded by YouTubers and internet personalities Logan Paul and KSI in partnership with Congo Brands. It is based in Louisville, Kentucky. Why Choose Prime Hydration Drinks?
Some of the benefits associated with the Prime Hydration drinks are:
Hydration and Electrolyte Replacement: The combination of electrolytes found in Prime Hydration drinks, such as sodium, potassium, and magnesium, helps to replace the electrolytes lost through sweat when exercising. It promotes appropriate fluid balance and hydration.
Enhanced Performance and Endurance: Prime Hydration's carbs give muscles a source of energy, which can help prolong exercise-induced exhaustion and enhance endurance. This can improve one's physical performance in general.
Less Soreness and Faster Muscle Recovery: Amino acids like glutamine, which are found in Prime Hydration, can help speed up muscle recovery and lessen soreness after exercise. This allows the body's healing mechanisms.
Delicious and easy: Prime Hydration is a tasty and easy alternative for on-the-go hydration because it is available in a range of enticing flavours in a ready-to-drink format.
Beneficial for Health: Prime drinks contain ingredients like vitamins, minerals, and amino acids, which provide health benefits to consumers.
Explore the Best Prime Hydration Drinks on Ubuy Mexico

Prime Energy Drink

The Prime Tropical-Punch hydration drink contains 10% coconut water, BCAAs, antioxidants, vitamin B, and electrolytes. It has only 25 calories with no added sugars, but each can contain 200 milligrams of caffeine, which can be beneficial for people who have an active lifestyle.
Lemon-Lime Prime
Lemon-Lime Prime is a delicious and hydrating drink. Its combination of electrolytes and carbohydrates boosts performance and hydration while quenching thirst. It is the ideal partner for your fitness journey because of its tangy lemon-lime flavour, which gives you a rush of energy and a sense of accomplishment with every sip.

Prime Sports Drink is the perfect combination of carbohydrates and electrolytes. It is known for its hydrating qualities during physical exercise. Frequently Asked Questions About Prime Hydration
Is Prime Hydration healthy?
Yes, Prime Hydration is a healthy option. It is lower in sugar and caffeine and has added coconut water, electrolytes, antioxidants, and BCAAs.
Are Prime Energy drinks suitable for daily consumption?
No, Prime Energy drinks are not suitable for daily consumption because of their high caffeine content. Too much caffeine can cause various health issues, such as insomnia, an increase in heart rate, anxiety, and dehydration. Thus, it is recommended that it be consumed with care.
